title: Grateful Dead Live at Nassau Coliseum on 1992-03-13
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step, The Same Thing, Brown Eyed Women, El Paso, Candyman, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Bird Song

Set 2

Way To Go Home, Crazy Fingers, Women Are Smarter, Wave To The Wind-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> Wharf Rat, Throwing Stones-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: Box Of Rain

reviews.review_text: BOOOOOORING what a total dud of a show
